OL,6,FRevised plans for new, bigger, Welsh
OL,7,FParliament constituencies have been
OL,8,Frevealed after a public consultation.
OL,10,FThe Democracy and Boundary Commission
OL,11,FCymru has proposed 16 constituencies
OL,12,Fby pairing Wales' 32 UK parliamentary
OL,13,Fconstituencies with a selected
OL,14,Fneighbour.
