OL,6,FIn choosing the new boundaries, the
OL,7,FCommission said it considered local
OL,8,Fties such as shared history, the Welsh
OL,9,Flanguage and socio-economic
OL,10,Fconsiderations in a bid to create
OL,11,Fconstituencies which feel "as natural
OL,12,Fas possible" to people across Wales.
OL,14,FThe 16 constituencies proposed by the
OL,15,FCommission:
OL,17,FAfter an initial consultation period,
OL,18,Fwhich saw more than 3,700 responses,
OL,19,Fthe Commission has made significant
OL,20,Fchanges to its proposed names.
