OL,3,CProposed Senedd constituency names
OL,4,Cdivides opinion
OL,6,FHe said: "This move is quite wrong.
OL,7,FWhile it may suit some parts of Wales
OL,8,Fto have Welsh-only names, places like
OL,9,Fthe Vale of Glamorgan and Bridgend are
OL,10,Fmajority English-speaking and the
OL,11,Fconstituency names should reflect
OL,12,Fthis."
OL,14,FHaving published its Revised
OL,15,FProposals, the Democracy and Boundary
OL,16,FCommission Cymru has opened a final 4-
OL,17,Fweek consultation to seek the views of
OL,18,Fpeople across Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
