OL,6,FThe Commission is keen to understand
OL,7,Fwhether there is public support for
OL,8,Fthese revised proposals or whether
OL,9,Fpeople feel that their parliamentary
OL,10,Fconstituency should instead be paired
OL,11,Fwith a different constituency.
OL,13,FThe Commission also looks forward to
OL,14,Fhearing the public's views on the much-
OL,15,Fchanged proposed constituency names.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
