OL,6,FShereen Williams, Chief Executive of
OL,7,Fthe Democracy and Boundary Commission
OL,8,FCymru, said: "These Revised Proposals
OL,9,Frepresent a significant step on the
OL,10,Fjourney to creating Wales's new
OL,11,Fconstituencies.
OL,13,F"The Commission would like to thank
OL,14,Fthe thousands of people who responded
OL,15,Fto the Initial Consultation, and
OL,16,Finvites everyone with a view on these
OL,17,Fproposals to let the Commission know
OL,18,Ftheir thoughts before 13 January 2025.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
