OL,3,CProposed Senedd constituency names
OL,4,Cdivides opinion
OL,6,F"The rules in place for this review
OL,7,Fmean that certain proposals can't be
OL,8,Fchanged, but following the feedback we
OL,9,Freceived from the public, we have made
OL,10,Fsignificant adjustments to the
OL,11,Fproposed names, as well as changing
OL,12,Fthe configuration of constituencies in
OL,13,Fthe Cardiff area.
OL,15,F"The Commission remains open to making
OL,16,Ffurther changes, depending on the
OL,17,Frepresentations we receive during this
OL,18,Fconsultation, so we urge everyone to
OL,19,Fshare their views before 13 January
OL,20,F2025."
